The Recursed is a multi chain project with provenance on two blockchains. Bitcoin and Solana. Using recursion we shall usher in a future filled with assets that communicate across chain and interact with them in perpetuity. From the immutable, to the non fungible, The Recursed shall rise and be resurrected. Powered by the Solana Stones, TheTickerIsRunes, and the ord library. 

The Metadata Shall be updated, post mint.

Using recursion we shall usher in a future filled with assets that communicate across chain and interact with them in perpetuity. From the immutable, to the non fungible, The Recursed shall rise and be resurrected. Powered by the Solana Stones, TheTickerIsRunes, and the ord library. 

The Metadata Shall be updated, post mint.
